<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Email Verification - WatchZone</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #0c274f;
        }

        p {
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #001f3f;
        }

        .text-link {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1>Email Verification - WatchZone</h1>
    <p>Thank you for signing up! Please verify your email address by clicking the link below:</p>
    <a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="button">Verify Email</a>
    <p>If you are unable to click the button, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
    <p><a href="{{verificationUrl}}" class="text-link">{{verificationUrl}}</a></p>
    <p>If you did not sign up for this account, please ignore this email.</p>
</body>

</html>